chen</b>"]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt31\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/do\" title=\"do\">do</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/perform\" title=\"perform\">perform</a>, <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/carry_out\" title=\"carry out\">carry out</a> (an action) <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren\" about=\"#mwt32\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\" about=\"#mwt32\">to execute<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">;</span> to put into operation</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren\" about=\"#mwt32\">)</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"<b>Mach</b> es<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>","translation":"<b>Do</b> it!"},{"example":"Das <b>hat</b> er ganz allein <b>gemacht</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>","translation":"He <b>did</b> that all by himself!"},{"example":"ein Experiment <b>machen</b>","translation":"to <b>perform</b> an experiment"}],"examples":["<b>Mach</b> es<span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>","Das <b>hat</b> er ganz allein <b>gemacht</b><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\">!</span>","ein Experiment <b>machen</b>"]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt37\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/do\" title=\"do\">do</a> (a noun); <span class=\"use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt38\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">indicates an activity associated with a noun</span>","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Sport <b>machen</b>","translation":"<b>do</b> sports"},{"example":"eine Party <b>machen</b>","translation":"<b>have</b> a party"}],"examples":["Sport <b>machen</b>","eine Party <b>machen</b>"]},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt41\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/go\" title=\"go\">go</a> (a specified sound) <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren\" about=\"#mwt42\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\" about=\"#mwt42\">to